Program: Last Word
Title: Seve Ballesteros, Richard Holmes, Dana Wynter, Enid Seeney and John Walker
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b010y0qv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 May 2011
Matthew Bannister on Seve Ballesteros - hailed as Europe's finest golfer - we speak to his former caddy and hear about his overwhelming compulsion to win. Professor Richard Holmes - the military historian and territorial army brigadier who brought to life great battles on TV. We have a tribute from General Sir Mike Jackson. Dana Wynter the actress best known for her role in Invasion of the Bodysnatchers And Enid Seeney, the designer who brought us the iconic 1950s Homemaker pottery. Show less